reviews.review_text: I go to McDonalds store. Food is always fresh and hot. Always have the desserts available. Customer service is great all the time. Love it when it checks off all your criterias
I do uber eats. One day at night its heavy rain and one staff offer me a coffee. I am fully wetted. I like their kindness.

Came here early August. Cleanest McDonald s I ve been to in the GVRD in a while. Team seems super on it. Food was was as good as Macdonald s can be, which honestly is a lot better then some of the Dons around New West / Burnaby.

Mcdonalds is a great place to eat and relax in their dining area. I wont call it a restaurant. The food is delicious and thats the dilemma.  Ive gained weight and had to buy a whole lot of new clothes. Ive lost control of my eating habits, and now Im paying the price. Im so fat people say hello to me twice. I highly recommend Mcdonalds to everyone looking for a great food experience

These guys are husslers! Maybe because those new self serve machines could be taking their jobs. I dont know. I never eat here and I was quite impressed. All the employees were efficient with a smile. Honestly it seemed like a happy environment. I was treated well and the food was hot and fresh.
Great iced coffee. Quick service. I need this after my gambling sessions
Always fresh, the only mcdonalds I have ever been to that is consistant. They deserve a special shout out because most are horrible.
Amazing location amazing food and coffee love mcdonalds

This is definitely the McDonalds of choice in my area. Theyre fast and efficient, have an awesome upstairs dining area if your staying to eat and Ive never had any issues with my order. Thanks guys keep up the great work!

Wow! I never had vanilla cone served perfectly. Perfect swirl and right temp not melting. I noticed the kitchen is very clean. Im not sure if they had renovated it but I saw some branch they remodeled the kitchen.

Love this Mcdonalds branch. Seems like after their renovations theservice became faster and more efficient. Staff are friendly and energetic. Always order here on my to work. Thumbs up . Keep up the good work .

Your friendly neighbourhood MacDonalds!! The only thing I am not fond of is  that if you enter via 8th, you may have to wait a while and youre at the mercy of the other guys coming in via McBride to let you in, as they only have to turn right into the line-up while you will have to hang a left, and you cant wait in front of the car park entrance. Otherwise, the staff is super friendly, and the queue seems to move at a good pace. If you do curbside pickup, you usually dont have to wait more than about 5 minutes.
The current staff at this location are excellent. Very nice to deal with.

The first thing I noticed is that an employee cleaned the table before I sat down. My order was completed quickly and the employees were friendly. Then, I accidentally dropped the bag containing my order and the fries spilled all over the floor (for which I profusely apologized). The employees were very gracious and cleaned it up and immediately gave me a new order of fries without me even asking! The epitome of service. Ive been to many, many McDonalds locations and this one ranks highly.
Nice place and closed room good for meetings and safe for kids

We came in with a large group late at night. To be honest we also had a rather difficult order due to food allergies. Most locations mess something up, so we always check our order before we leave. This location however killed it! They were quick, got our order correct on the first try and were super friendly. I wish we could tip fast food employees because the staff really deserved it.

These guys are great. Last night due to mid communication, they did not charge me for 2 ice-cream sundae. today I went back to pay them, they did not accept it, much appreciated. I bought two fries, and the staff asked if I want any sauce? I just wanted one and fast so I said whatever is available, so she has put one from each type. Tunnels a lot
I went ther around 11pm on Thursday ,it was super busy and fast too. The girl working at window **Nav**   shes super nice and well spoken..Definitely will go back ther next.. ...

Come here everyday the staff are incredible and awesome always fast efficiency  today my car stalled in their drive thru they helped pushed my car to a safe spot thanks mcbride McDonalds your pretty awesome staff
Smaller restaurant good service.

A pretty busy place and there are often waits for food, but as its a hot spot for late night dine-ins and a permanently busy drive-through  it makes sense. Good service, my orders have been correct and I was even offered additional food to make up for waiting for my order. Nothing to complain about for this location.

Arrived at McDonalds after it had already closed its main doors however it would allow me to order off the app and then pick up from the window if they can do this why cant they just take the order at the window?

This McDonalds is much better than the one at Royal City Centre due to faster service and much better quality of food. The restaurant in this location is also much cleaner. The staff working here are also very polite, patient and straight-forward. Great McDonalds location for family and kids.
Great service love the food understandable of wait time especially with a big family I have and especially when it busy

Todays associate Eric was one of the friendliest and helpful associates I ever dealt with. There was a lineup at the counter so he took our order at the self order kiosk and even offered to bring our order to us when it was ready. This was a mini lifesaver as I was there with my 4 yr old at a busy time and I was able to find a table, get him seated and watch him while our food was prepared and brought out. He even offered to check if they had more happy meal toys when he overheard my son say he already had the toy that he was given. The food wasnt bad either and it was a good experience overall, thanks to Eric!

Excellent service. We ordered 600 apple pies for our company event and not only they had the pies ready on time the crew even helped me bring them to my car and packaged them neatly. Despite speaking to different managers for this event, there weren t any communication gaps. Kudos to this team.

MITSLAL is good crew member she does know what she is doing because of her this McDonalds customer service good. But these days their coffee quality not good. I pass 2 McDonalds to enjoy their coffee but not anymore.

I usually swing through here on my way to work between 530am-830am on weekdays for coffee. I come from Surrey & its on my way to the highway. My coffee has only been wrong once in all the time Ive come here. The morning crew is efficient & gets us through very fast. Also, I have an oversized truck (with an arrow board above it) and I can fit through the drivethru.

Leaving a positive review where it is due, went drive thru for coffee in a pretty busy early morning rush yesterday, the Customer Service lady in the window was awesome. Happy, helpful, positive. Its so rare these days to experience that, I thought I should make special mention of it. Thanks

I went through the drive thru during the night to grab myself some coffee and I was helped by Shantal. I was pleased to see how her customer service skills were. Shantal was really kind and professional towards me and the customers that were in front of me. If anyone ever gets a chance, you should get help from her. Shes the best!!!!!

Very quick drive thru service. Ordered 20 McNuggets. The nuggets were delicious, fresh and steaming out of the fryer!!!!! My only complaint is that it was hard to hear the drive-thru girl in the pouring rain but she ended up getting my order right :) I would 10/10 drive-thru again in the future!!
Very clean and friendly staff. Should be one of the best McDonald in Vancouver area. They have 2 floors and we ll maintained.

We drive specifically out of our way to go to this location in hopes that Kyle will be serving us at the drive through window. The quickest draw in the West, he is speedy, polite, and funny as hell. He expects as much attention to detail from his coworkers and teammates and is always on them to produce the quickest and best service. Hands down the best Macdonalds to go to when youre in a hurry and in need of a good laugh!

Staff is very friendly, the food is served in a timely manner and the best part is that their ice cream machine works. There is a decent sized play place for kids upstairs, and the restaurant is nice an quiet at times.

Even though they completely forgot my order, they did come out with an apple pie. The poor girl had to listen to me bark about waiting an extra 15 min. I wait longer in traffic lol. Great job guys and gals!
It was a great experience visiting there. Staff was very friendly. I recommend to tip staff members if possible.
I go to the drive thru on my way to work and the morning crew are great and very friendly. Alway a long line but they move it along really quickly. Order is always correct.

The McDonalds on McBride street in New Westminster has the most awesome and friendly staff. Seriously every time i go there no matter what time it is i am met with a genuine smile and happy employees. Same food as any other Micky Ds but the staff make this one my favorite.

Hit the drive thru on my way home to Port Moody with low expectations. I ve dealt with the Austin Rd location for years and they re terrible. I was surprised to find the guy running the orders had great energy and the food was as perfect as you d ever hope!
Amazing service! Thank you Food
Actually, Mcs alwats welcome when I am busy. qtr pound with cheese!!!!! And fries are the answer!

Am not fan of fast food restaurant but sometimes coming here to drink tea and to let my kids have a good at play area, Their coffee is not better than Tim Hortons, as you can right now get an extra large for more $1, which includes a free refill and one of those stickers for a free coffee, effectively making it about 5 times cheaper than others. Their pastries are also better than tims. Good coupon system too.
Super quick friendly service and nuggets were extremely fresh. Finally super pleased with McDonalds location would recommend if youre in a hurry looking for good quality fast food
Great place for McDonalds breakfast.
The staff is great, I went through the drive thru when they had some system issue but they worked it out and served me what I wanted! Every other time Ive been here has been good
Came here at 9am on Boxing Day. Ordered 2 meals and upgraded to 2 hashbrowns each. With 6 cars in the drive thru lane. We got our food under 4mins and they were fresh :)

I went there for the first time this afternoon. The young man cleaning the tables and floor was working very hard and doing a great job. My partner is very very picky and she was impressed. It was the cleanest fast food restaurant Ive seen.
Look busy but got mobile order in reasonable time.  The management staff is very helpful and friendly.  Were there during lunch hour.
Young man at the drive thru was quick and accurate Also let me know my gas flap was open!! Thanks again.
The restaurant is very nice and clean,  they just finished a great renovation.
Friendly service Good workers Always very polite Food : 5/5

This was a good location. The restaurant was clean and the service was quick it lived up to the expectations that I have for a fast food McDonalds restaurant. The internet was strong where I sat and I was able to enjoy the complementary McDonalds internet that I now have come to expect at their locations. I have no complaints to report
We recently started visiting this Mc D for early breakfast and the guy named Eric working there greet us with a great smile that makes our day. Thanks Eric. Doing great.
Good food and customer service they made a mistake but apologized and fixed it rlly quick

Ive only eaten at the actual place like once and it looked like an above average McDonalds but the delivery is almost always good and accurate, I would know Ive ordered from this McDonalds about 80 times and now that Im moving back home I gotta tell them how good they are, 10/10 would order from again In all the orders Ive made the only mistakes was missing straw which they are pretty good with now, unlike the new west McDonalds that fills ur cup with ice instead of pop
good location. kindof weird to get into depending on which way ur coming from. drive thru is quick but always super busy. seating is a little tite but does have a play place.
Nicest workers I ve ever come across at a McDonald s. The drive thru, cashier, and person who brought my food out were all wonderful

I to give this McDonald s at 8th and McBride a 10 for customer service.  I locked my keys in my car and my cell phone was dead.  Having just relocated from Edmonton, AB to Abbotsford I  was stranded in New Westminster.   Assistant Manager, Fatima offered to charge my cell and took time to check on me from time to time during my 40 minute wait.  Guest Service Representive, Kyle went above and beyond by calling BCAA on his own card.  Their service, assistance and compassion in helping me in my situation was exemplary.
Recently renovated  2 levels restaurant,  plenty of parking, fast service,  well maintained washrooms.
Location is perfect, service was super fast, thanks for providing convenience!
Service is quick, I always skip the drive through
This Mcdonalds was closing at 12am and a group of us got there and they were Very polite and let us stay after closing. Well made my food as well. Thanks.
Drive-thru was a long line but the staff crushed it. Kind, quick, and accurate. I love the 24 hour drive-thru
good service. Very fast drive thru.
Alright, Im sick and tired of this McDonald s knocking it out of the park every time I come here. Seriously, send that friggen Michelin star chef on the night shift home.
Bacon egg english muffin from mcds is by far best in lower mainland..
Mc Donald s is always amazing!! Specially this one as they make your order up to perfection
They have fresh food here 9 out of 10 times
Orders can be done through a machine instead of a person, made the experience quick and seamless as compared to other McDonalds locations.
They are fast and polite. Sandwiches are good as always One of the best branches of Mcdonald s
I legit think this is one if the best McDonalds. Its always fresh and hot even if getting delivered.
It has nice parking place, and good playing area to your children, staffs are friendly. Nice to drink good coffee.
I always go to McDonalds with my friends. Its my favorite  place to go. Really amazing food and service! Staff are pleasant!
Stopped for some fries and a vanilla milkshake. Both were superb! Hit that spot
fast ,efficient drive through. Got what I ordered. Tasted like expected.
Ordered two sausage and Eggers at 2am and combined then to make a super sausage and Egger. Food coma! A good night sleep followed
This location has never messed up my drive thru order yet. Its a miracle.
Excellent customer service by management and employee Zackery and all the burgers were well sauced!
Thank you guys got my order super fast and correct i appreciate :) Carmen
One of best McDonalds in New WESTMINSTER. McDonalds in Surrey are worst... Food : 5/5
I was short 25 cents and the young man at the window put my order through anyways.  Id forgot to bring my wallet with debit/credit cards.
This is probably one of my favourite McDonalds locations. Food, service, and cleanliness are always top notch compared to other McDonalds near me.
Nice but they should have a shed to protect us when ordering and picking up on raining days.
Quick drive thru that hasnt messed my order up. ever. Keep the good work up!
A great McDonalds. Recently renovated, lots of seating.
Early morning drive thru staff always great.
Staff are pleasant, I ordered chicken nuggets, enjoyed the nuggets & dip. The prices are very reasonable.
Ive had great service and food here
Our favourite McDonald s, great staff, play area for kids! We even had my son s 3rd birthday here!
Excellent place for meals. Friendly environment and nice employee.
Great food, good for a quick snack and bite. Dont eat too  much of it as its unhealthy.
Amazing staff and guests service, one of the best McDonalds Ive ever been.
Nice place with very good customers service
Very pleasant. The staff is efficient and friendly.
gave my drive through order to someone else, 10/10 would have wrong food again
Great service!
I always love my Mc Doubles and strawberry milk shakes Im always satisfied tbh
One is the best place to live beautiful girls great people honest to the most part its home. Please visit.
Top Notch Food. Should be considered 5 star dining.  I recommend the chicken with the potatoes.
As always, my favorite hunger savior. Tasty Fillet o fish meal...easy on the pocket.
